<html>
<!-- We usually add styling css element in the head tag under title tag . We use style tag for adding css element and inside style tag we add the tag to be styled ( here we style the p tag which stands for the paragraph Tag ) -->
<head><title>To learn CSS</title>
<style>
p{font-size: 28px}
</style>
</head>
<body>
	<p style="color:green"> Hello World </p>
	<!-- The Above Method Shows How To add one quick styling element to a Tag
	-->
</body>
</html>
